name: Colored Coin (dl)
description:
A Coin that you can fully customize: you can change it's color, coin value and even it's heal value.

Parameter 1: XBBBBBGGGGGRRRRR (bits)

B,G,R: Color

Parameter 2: OHVV

0: Heal or Hurt (0: Heal, 1: Hurt)
H: Heal/Hurt Value
V: Coin Value

Parameter 3: SFFF

S: Star ID
F: Amount of frames between damage
Note: set parameter 3 to 0 if you do not wish to place a Death Coin

Created by: Splatterboy

name: Yoshi NPC (dl)
description:
A Yoshi that stands around and can talk to the player.

Parameter 2: EMMM

M: Message ID of final message

Parameter 3: TBBBBBGGGGGRRRRR (bits)

T: 1 if this Yoshi should talk
B,G,R: Color

Ported by: Splatterboy

name: Character Block (dl)
description:
Permanently switches character without having to go to the character door or having to use caps.

1 - Character doesn't need to be unlocked

1 - Mario
2 - Luigi
3 - Wario
